data.description: Great House ! 2 story home, School within walking distance , extra wide lot.  Selling AS IS, room sizes estimated .  New Roof , New Siding , New Washer , Newer Mechanicals, plenty of room for a Large Family. Including a Full Basement with New Paneling. plenty of storage .  Enclosed porch ready for your evenings with Family, Outside  deck   attached to a huge Pool for your summer staycations . and a grand Patio  for the summer family gatherings. Property boasts a two car garage and an additional two car port . come take a look at the space and make it your home.
